entries.femaleVariant: Your thinking's sound. Won't get far in Night City without any.
What can I say. Tensions are flarin' up. Suits over in Corpo Plaza don't like that their view looks out over all us ordinary, working class people.
Something's comin', I can feel it. One firebomb and all of Vista'll go up in flames. And next morning, they'll hire us to build new offices on top of our burnt-out units.
